[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "一生挑戦しないなら、負け犬……かぁ。\nむむむ、あの王女様、痛いトコ突くなぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00183",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "姉様……大丈夫。私、犬も嫌いじゃない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00184",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ありがとうベップ、いつだって味方してくれて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00185",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "はぁ……アタシ、間違ったこと言ってないよね？\n普通に考えて、どこからどう見ても王女様は無謀だし？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00186",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あんな気持ちだけじゃどうにもならないのに、\nそれなのに……言い返せなかった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00187",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "本当はアタシも分かってるんだ。\n壁を乗り越えて先に進まなきゃいけないんだって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00188",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "アルビーナらしくないわね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00189",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ヤンネさん……仕事は？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00190",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "ちょっと抜けてきちゃった。\nこっちが緊急事態だしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00191",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "――ねえ、アルビーナ。\nいつものヤンチャなあなたはどこへ行ったの？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00192",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "ヤンチャ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00193",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "私を困らせてきたアルビーナは、そんなことで\n思い悩むようないい子じゃなかったでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00194",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "壁にぶつかって、乗り越えなきゃいけない。\n普通なら正面からぶつかろうとして思い悩む……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00195",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "でもあなたは違う。なんとか抜け道を見つけ出して\nやってきたじゃないの。私も何度説得されたか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00196",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "抜け道……かぁ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00197",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "でも、そうでしょう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00198",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "それは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00199",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（確かにそうだ。アタシは星の案内人としての天命を\n　捨てないまま、錬金術士として活動してきた）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00200",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（まあ、あれは師匠が裏で手を回したからだけど、\n　その特権をアタシはありがたく使わせてもらった）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00201",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（そっちがその気なら全力で乗っかってやる……\n　そう、それがアタシ、アルビちゃんだった！）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00202",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "今さら怖くなってまごまごしてるあなたを見るのは、\nいい加減我慢ならないわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00203",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "ヤ、ヤンネさん……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00204",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00205",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "小さい頃からアタシは「何者か」になりたかった。\n普通の人とは違う英雄のような存在にって、努力した",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00206",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でも、レスナに――本物の英雄に出会って、\n自分はぜんぜん普通なんすねって思い知らされた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00207",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "もちろん普通の平凡な生き方だって否定はしないよ。\n日陰でゆっくりとのんびりする気持ちよさも知ってる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00208",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "でもね……アタシはアルビーナ・ジムロック！\n日の目を見ないまま終わるなんてまっぴらごめん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00209",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "ふふ、そうこなくっちゃ。\nまだ若いんだから、変に達観しなくていいのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00210",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "後先を考えるのは大人の仕事。\nそれに、ベップちゃんだってついてるんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00211",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "７回転んだら、８回起き上がればいい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00212",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん……っていうか、思い出したらムカついてきた！\nヘルトの奴、アタシのこと馬鹿にしてさ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00213",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "言うに事欠いてこのアルビちゃんを\n「戦う意志のない一般人」って……！　ムカつく！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00214",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "一般人でも何者かになれるんだって、\n英雄になれるんだって、証明してやるんだから！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00215",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "怒りを原動力にして、開き直った姉様も素敵……\nかっこいい。惚れ直した",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00216",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あの、人を人と思わない蔑んだ視線……！\nなんとかインチキしてでもギャフンって言わせる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00217",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "やっとらしくなったわね、ふふっ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00218",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そうと決まったら、ちょっとアタシ\nここにカンヅメして対抗策を練るから！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00219",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "今さらかもしれないけど、ちょっとでもあいつに\n勝てる確率を上げるためにあがいておく！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00220",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "そう、分かったわ。\n夜食を作って、届けてあげる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00221",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "閃きを試したいときは、私のこと\n実験台にしていいから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00222",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "うん、協力ありがとっ！\nさーて、練って練って練りまくるぞー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00223",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "大丈夫、アタシはずる賢さならレスナに負けない！\nずるして、騙して、勝利を盗み取る！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_037_00224",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ヤンネ",
		"romanized_name": "Janne",
		"model_path_hash": "1819147851487138677",
		"text": "ほんと聖戦士としては聞き捨てならない発言だけど。\n私が焚きつけちゃったのよねぇ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_152_037_00225",
		"still_path_hash": "6181229795949782132",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "私の心は、すでに姉様に盗まれてる……\nとんでもない怪盗アルビーナ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_037_00226",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]